pos_mean_info_list.mean: 有效地；效率高地（efficient的副词形式）

word_mean_info__list.difference: “效率高的”，“有能力的”，用以指人或物，着重有效地利用时间、精力并取得预期效果。如：The German telephone system is highly efficient. (德国的电话系统效率很高。)
常用以指物，强调能产生某种预期的效果。如：effective medicine, effective method等。

yingyinNormal.en: Leonard, I was... What's Kripke doing here? Oh, he's just helping us develop a better, more efficient neutrino comm system that we're gonna pitch to the military, making yours obsolete.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱纳德，我... 克里普奇在这里干什么？他正在帮我们开发一种更好，更高效的中微子通讯系统我们就能联系军队，彻底打垮你。

yingyinNormal.en: Efficient in both preventative measures and tactical assault.
yingyinNormal.zh: 高效执行预防性举措和战术性进攻。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, while also getting in a solid dig at you. Pretty efficient?
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，我还同时好好挖苦了你一番，这才叫一石二鸟。

yingyinNormal.en: Human form isn't efficient, biologically speaking, we're out-moded, but he keeps coming back to it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人体结构并不高效，生物学上来说，我们是过时的，但他一直想复生为人。

yingyinNormal.en: In particular, this allows it to have an echo location system that is more efficient than any Sonar invented by mankind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尤其是这让它们拥有回声定位系统，比人类发明的声纳装置更有效率。

yingyinNormal.en: Good. I need you to be careful and efficient. And remember, if I'm harsh with you, it is only because you're doing it wrong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好 ，你们要小心一点，同时动作要快。记住，如果我朝你们叫唤，那肯定是你们哪里做错了。

yingyinNormal.en: That's gonna leave us shorthanded. Oh, I can automate most of the park's safety protocols, Mr. Stubbs. How efficient of you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这会让我们人手不足。我可以让园区大部分的安全协议自动执行。斯塔布斯先生，您可真是效率十足。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 功效；效力；效能；效力的提高；效率
adj. 效率高的；有能力的；能胜任的；防止造成…的浪费的

sense_info_list.en: achieving maximum productivity with minimum wasted effort or expense, especially of a system or machine

examination_example.sentence: When our brains switch between being focused and unfocused on a task, they tend to be more <highlight>efficient</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当我们的大脑在专注和不专注于一项任务之间切换时，它们往往会更有效率。

examination_example.sentence: Deep reading requires not just time, but a special kind of time which can't be obtained merely by becoming more <highlight>efficient</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 深度阅读需要的不仅仅是时间，而是一种特别的时间，它并不是仅仅通过提高效率就能获得的。

examination_example.sentence: Although electronic means of payment may be more <highlight>efficient</highlight> than a payments system based on paper, several factors work against the disappearance of the paper system.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽管电子支付方式可能比基于纸张的支付系统更高效，但有几个因素阻碍了纸质系统的消亡。

"效率高的"，"有能力的"，用以指人或物，着重有效地利用时间、精力并取得预期效果。如：The German telephone system is highly efficient. (德国的电话系统效率很高。)
